data.name: lblAboutUs.Text
data.value:
A sprawling sanctuary bounded by shimmering emerald waters and ivory sand, and shaded by tall, rustling palms, Octopus stretches across six hectares on Cebu's stunning Mactan Island. Just a 20-minute drive from the international airport, our resort is designed for romantic getaways, family vacations and guests looking to enjoy laidback tropical elegance. Forty expansive villas offer luxurious comfort, outfitted with private plunge pools and earth-toned furniture by Cebu’s multi-awarded designers. Octopus also offers 250 guestrooms that combine modern conveniences with neo-Asian décor and contemporized native accents.
You may have a hard time deciding where to start at Octopus. The resort offers an infinity pool that blends right in with the serene Hilutungan Channel, four restaurants and bars, a wide range of water activities plus opportunities for leisurely inactivity, including indulgent treatments at Aum Spa. Snorkel, swim or ride a banana boat? Maybe a nap on the beach? Lounge chairs are sprinkled by the pool and along the enclave of white sand out front. Fine coral reefs are only a few minutes away by speedboat. And taking advantage of our prime beachside location, we offer kayaking and jet skiing in addition to island-hopping tours and scuba diving trips. Once the sun descends, take in a pre-dinner cocktail at the chic Azure Beach Club before meandering across the resort's manicured grounds. Whatever you choose, Octopus assures authentic, memorable experiences in a delightfully unique setting.
